{"tid":103872,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)曬撚氣1-2","createTime":"2017-02-01T15:58:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-01T18:59:58.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1fd7cd797164e415a519f30f3fb772654206d11b","tid":103872,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T15:58:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=zkxYWYOkbsQg7WdKzXEy6U%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=38b198db\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> 關左ADBLOCK可以睇到V台好似係 按左下可轉CC台<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=zkxYWYOkbsQg7WdKzXEy6U%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=ae8ed542\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a>可以直接睇到V台<br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/c/c2/鬼魅山房2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fc%2Fc2%2F%E9%AC%BC%E9%AD%85%E5%B1%B1%E6%88%BF2.jpg&h=9d47039a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/5/57/Silent_hill.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F5%2F57%2FSilent_hill.jpg&h=2ea57286&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.蘿絲（Rose Da Silva）自小收養的女兒雪倫（Sharon Da Silva）患有夢遊症且多次提及小鎮『沉默之丘』。為尋求答案，蘿絲不顧丈夫克里斯席瓦（Christopher Da Silva）的反對於一天晚上帶著雪倫前往沉默之丘。在接近小鎮時二人被女警西碧兒（Cybil Bennett）追捕（因懷疑蘿絲企圖遺棄雪倫），蘿絲於驅車擺脫追捕時突然看見一女孩在路上出現，為閃避而撞上路邊失去知覺。蘿絲於醒來時發現雪倫竟已失蹤，白霧籠罩著一切，無數灰燼從天上持續地飄落。<br />\n<br />\n蘿絲為尋回雪倫而在荒無一人的街上尋找，除首次經歷沉默之丘表世界（Fog world）和裏世界（Otherworld）的交替，也遇到一名為妲麗亞（Dahlia Gillespie）的婦人。妲麗亞告訴蘿絲其女兒亞萊莎（Alessa Gillespie）被村民虐待，並在看見雪倫的相片後認為她就是亞萊莎。蘿絲擺脫妲麗亞後回到車子欲聯絡丈夫但遇上西碧兒，西碧兒發現雪倫失蹤後拘捕蘿絲帶回警署，但在徒步回程時發現道路被斷崖取代。二人只得繼續在鎮上尋找出路...<br />\n<br />\n2.海瑟梅森和父親哈利梅森一直以來都在躲避不明力量的恐怖追殺。她18歲生日當晚，在夢魘纏身和父親神秘失蹤的詭譎情況下，海瑟發現自己原來從未瞭解「真正的自己」。隨著啟示錄的指引，她踏入了一個危機四伏、狂暴絕倫，可能令她永世不得脫身的邪惡世界&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n12 00AM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f59e02265faf91f860d0180909473061f8c67c1d","tid":103872,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T16:07:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"050db25509f6ef7517169d72e9e44d4aba1aff88","tid":103872,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T16:35:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15d33c638d254c04a3922434686b9d48fff5c3b9","tid":103872,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T17:19:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a19c89cd80479b355ce64b5b0544a37ebd7ddbd3","tid":103872,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T18:59:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}